  "id": "html-1771913809844",
  "title": "Seguimiento sistemático a los RAE",
  "type": "html",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Justificación - Oferta Internacional - Unitrópico</title>\n  <!-- Fuente Montserrat y CSS base -->\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css_presentaciones/unitropico_base.css\">\n  <style>\n    /* =========================\n       ESTILOS ADICIONALES\n    ========================= */\n    html,\n    body {\n      height: 100%;\n      margin: 0;\n      overflow-x: hidden;\n      background: url(\"../img/background-1.jpg\") no-repeat center center fixed;\n      background-size: cover;\n      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    /* Navbar */\n    .navbar-img {\n      width: 100%;\n      background: var(--verde-1);\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .navbar-img img {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: auto;\n      max-height: 110px;\n      object-fit: contain;\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    /* Contenedor principal */\n    .container {\n      max-width: 1100px;\n      margin: 30px auto;\n      padding: 0 25px;\n    }\n\n    /* Estilos para Estrategias de flexibilización */\n    .section-header-line {\n      margin-bottom: 40px;\n      text-align: center;\n      padding-top: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .section-header-line h2 {\n      font-weight: 400;\n      font-size: 2.2rem;\n      line-height: 1.35;\n      color: #007580;\n      margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n    }\n\n    /* Estilos para el Icono Lateral */\n    .comp-icon-row {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      margin-top: 80px;\n      margin-bottom: 90px;\n      gap: 30px;\n    }\n\n    .comp-icon-container {\n      width: 140px;\n      height: 140px;\n      background-color: #fcfcfc;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08), inset 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);\n      border: 3px solid #f2f2f2;\n    }\n\n    .comp-icon-container img {\n      width: 55%;\n      height: auto;\n    }\n\n    .comp-text-title {\n      font-size: 2.2rem;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      color: #007580;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .container {\n        margin: 15px;\n        padding: 0 15px;\n      }\n\n      .comp-icon-row {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        gap: 15px;\n      }\n\n      .comp-text-title {\n        font-size: 1.8rem;\n      }\n\n      .section-header-line h2 {\n        font-size: 1.5rem !important;\n      }\n\n      .line-gold {\n        width: 100% !important;\n        max-width: 550px;\n      }\n\n      .line-gray {\n        width: 80% !important;\n        max-width: 450px;\n      }\n    }\n\n    /* =========================================\n       NUEVO LAYOUT: SEGUIMIENTO SISTEMATICO RAE (12 NODOS)\n       ========================================= */\n    .rae-header {\n      margin-top: 50px;\n      margin-bottom: 50px;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .rae-header h2 {\n      font-weight: 700;\n      font-size: 2.3rem;\n      color: #007580;\n      margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n    }\n\n    .perf-container {\n      position: relative;\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 1000px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      height: 600px;\n      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    .perf-svg {\n      position: absolute;\n      top: 0; left: 0;\n      width: 100%; height: 100%;\n      z-index: 1;\n      pointer-events: none;\n    }\n\n    .perf-node {\n      position: absolute;\n      width: 96px;\n      height: 96px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      text-align: center;\n      color: white;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      font-size: 0.75rem;\n      line-height: 1.2;\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n      z-index: 5;\n      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n    }\n\n    .perf-center {\n      position: absolute;\n      width: 140px;\n      height: 140px;\n      background-color: #89797d; /* grayish purple */\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      top: 300px;\n      left: 500px;\n      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      text-align: center;\n      color: white;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      font-size: 0.9rem;\n      border: 4px solid white;\n      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n      z-index: 10;\n    }\n\n    .bg-teal { background-color: #00594e; }\n    .bg-gold { background-color: #bfa773; }\n\n    @media (max-width: 900px) {\n      .perf-container {\n        height: auto;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        justify-content: center;\n        gap: 15px;\n        padding-bottom: 50px;\n      }\n      .perf-svg { display: none; }\n      .perf-node, .perf-center {\n        position: static;\n        transform: none !important;\n        width: 120px;\n        height: 120px;\n        font-size: 0.85rem;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <!-- Navbar de imagen -->\n  <div class=\"navbar-img\">\n    <img src=\"media/denominacion/navbar.png\" alt=\"Navbar Unitropico\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <!-- Título del artículo (alineado izquierda) -->\n    <div class=\"top-left-title subtitulo text-verde-1\">\n      <span class=\"text-bronce-1\">2.5.3.2.3.2.4. Aspectos curriculares -</span> e) Mecanismos de Evaluación\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Encabezado centrado -->\n    <div class=\"rae-header\">\n      <h2>Seguimiento sistemático a los RAE</h2>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0px;\">\n        <div class=\"line-gold\" style=\"width: 450px; height: 3px; background-color: #ba9b5e; border-radius: 2px;\"></div>\n        <div class=\"line-gray\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 6px; background-color: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 3px;\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Contenedor Radial 12 Nodos -->\n    <div class=\"perf-container\">\n      \n      <svg class=\"perf-svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 600\">\n        <!-- Lines linking center (500, 300) to each calculated position -->\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"90\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"605\" y2=\"118.2\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"681.8\" y2=\"195\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"710\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"681.8\" y2=\"405\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"605\" y2=\"481.8\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"510\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"395\" y2=\"481.8\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"318.2\" y2=\"405\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"318.2\" y2=\"195\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"395\" y2=\"118.2\" stroke=\"#4c779e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n      </svg>\n\n      <!-- Center Node -->\n      <div class=\"perf-center\">\n        Instrumentos<br>evaluación<br>del<br>desempeño<br>RAE\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Perimeter Nodes (Clockwise starting from 12 o'clock) -->\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-gold\" style=\"top: 90px; left: 500px;\">Portafolio<br>y<br>E-Portafolio</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-teal\" style=\"top: 118.2px; left: 605px;\">Estudio<br>de caso</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-gold\" style=\"top: 195px; left: 681.8px;\">Proyectos<br>o trabajos<br>finales</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-teal\" style=\"top: 300px; left: 710px;\">Informe o<br>reportes de<br>prácticas</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-gold\" style=\"top: 405px; left: 681.8px;\">Mapa<br>Mental</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-teal\" style=\"top: 481.8px; left: 605px;\">Debate</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-gold\" style=\"top: 510px; left: 500px;\">Ensayo</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-teal\" style=\"top: 481.8px; left: 395px;\">Exposición<br>oral</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-gold\" style=\"top: 405px; left: 318.2px;\">Exámenes<br>(escritos y<br>orales)</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-teal\" style=\"top: 300px; left: 290px;\">Tareas y<br>ejercicios</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-gold\" style=\"top: 195px; left: 318.2px;\">Lecturas</div>\n      <div class=\"perf-node bg-teal\" style=\"top: 118.2px; left: 395px;\">Foros de<br>discusión</div>\n      \n    </div>\n</body>\n\n</html>",
  "allowScripts": true,
  "hotspots": []
}